graph LR
    TrustyAI[TrustyAI Service Operator]

    %% External Dependencies - Required
    TrustyAI -->|deploys| TrustyAIServiceImage[TrustyAI Service 0.25+<br/>Quarkus]

    %% External Dependencies - Optional
    TrustyAI -.->|persistence| PostgreSQL[PostgreSQL 13+<br/>5432/TCP]
    TrustyAI -.->|LLM eval framework| LMEvalHarness[EleutherAI<br/>lm-eval-harness]
    TrustyAI -.->|experiment tracking| MLFlow[MLFlow 2.x<br/>5000/TCP]
    TrustyAI -.->|guardrails framework| FMSGuardrails[FMS Guardrails 0.x]
    TrustyAI -.->|LLM safety| NemoGuardrails[NVIDIA NeMo Guardrails]
    TrustyAI -.->|observability| OpenTelemetry[OpenTelemetry 1.x]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    TrustyAI -->|monitors inferences| KServe[KServe<br/>Model Serving]
    TrustyAI -->|retrieves metadata| ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>gRPC API]
    TrustyAI -.->|UI integration| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
    TrustyAI -.->|sidecar deployment| ModelServing[Model Serving Infrastructure]
    TrustyAI -.->|job execution| DSPipelines[Data Science Pipelines]

    %% External Services
    TrustyAI -->|model downloads| HuggingFace[HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    TrustyAI -->|datasets & results| S3[S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]

    %% Platform Dependencies
    TrustyAI -->|orchestration| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
    TrustyAI -.->|metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Metrics Collection]
    TrustyAI -.->|TLS certs| CertManager[cert-manager]

    %% Integration Points - Bidirectional
    Dashboard -->|manage services| TrustyAI
    DSPipelines -->|execute eval jobs| TrustyAI
    KServe -->|inference data| TrustyAI

